OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FAs friends of Absi Ahmed Mohammad,
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to "a bright, kind, funny
OL,8,Fyoung man with his whole future ahead
OL,9,Fof him", an inquest has heard the 17-
OL,10,Fyear old drowned while swimming in
OL,11,FHigh Dam Tarn with his friends on
OL,12,FApril 7th 2026.
OL,14,FCumbria Coroner's Court, held in
OL,15,FWorkington, heard the teenager, known
OL,16,Fas Absi Ahmed, was from Poulton-le-
OL,17,FFylde and had got into difficulty
OL,18,Fbefore disappearing below the water.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/14
