FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FCumbria Police were called at 12.32pm,
OL,7,Fsparking a multi-agency response
OL,8,Finvolving the Coastguard, Mountain
OL,9,FRescue, Fire Service, Ambulance
OL,10,FService and Police. Professional
OL,11,Fdivers recovered his body at 8:57pm
OL,12,Fthat evening.
OL,14,FThe Coroner's Court heard that the
OL,15,Fmedical cause of death was drowning,
OL,16,Fdetermined following a CT scan and
OL,17,Fpost-mortem.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe Assistant Coroner, Dr Nicholas
OL,7,FShaw, told the court, "This is clearly
OL,8,Fa tragic and unnatural death, and
OL,9,Ftherefore an inquest is required." He
OL,10,Fadjourned the inquest to establish the
OL,11,Fcircumstances around Absi's death
OL,12,Funtil the provisional date of
OL,13,FSeptember 1st 2026, awaiting
OL,14,Fstatements from police, witnesses, and
OL,15,Fthe North West Ambulance Service.
OL,26,@oD@WOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FA fundraising page set up by his
OL,7,Ffriends has raised almost #16,000 to
OL,8,Fsupport his parents and other causes
OL,9,Fclose to the family's hearts, saying
OL,10,Ftheir world has been changed forever;
OL,11,F"His passing has left a deep and
OL,12,Funimaginable pain in the hearts of his
OL,13,Fparents and his brother, as well as
OL,14,Fthe many friends who adored him."
OL,16,FIt was set up by those calling
OL,17,Fthemselves "four boys who were lucky
OL,18,Fenough to call Absi our best mate...
OL,19,FWe grew up together, made memories
OL,20,Fwe'll never forget, and planned a
OL,21,Ffuture we thought we'd all be part of."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FThey continue, "It still doesn't feel
OL,7,Freal that he's gone. He was the person
OL,8,Fwho made everything better, the one
OL,9,Fwho made us laugh, the one who brought
OL,10,Feveryone together, the one who never
OL,11,Flet anyone feel left out. Absi wasn't
OL,12,Fjust our mate. He was our brother."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FThey paid tribute to him as, "someone
OL,7,Fwho brought warmth and laughter
OL,8,Fwherever he went... He had this way of
OL,9,Fwalking into a room and changing the
OL,10,Fwhole mood with his smile. He was
OL,11,Ffunny without trying, kind without
OL,12,Fthinking, and loyal in a way you don't
OL,13,Foften see at our age... His loss has
OL,14,Fshaken our entire community."
OL,16,FAs well as helping the family, the
OL,17,Ffundraiser also seeks to provide funds
OL,18,Ffor equipment the family is now
OL,19,Fcalling for.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe 19th century tarn, High Dam, is
OL,7,Fpopular for swimming and woodland
OL,8,Fwalks. Absi's family are now urging
OL,9,Fauthorities to improve safety at the
OL,10,Fsite.
OL,12,FThe family say they do not blame
OL,13,Fanyone for his death but say "there
OL,14,Fneeds to be more warning signs and
OL,15,Flifesaving equipment to try to prevent
OL,16,Fanother tragedy."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FAbsi's brother Adil said: "My family
OL,7,Fdoesn't want another parent or family
OL,8,Fmember to lose someone like this. We
OL,9,Fwant to make sure that if someone gets
OL,10,Finto difficulty in the future ` like
OL,11,FAbsi did ` people there have more
OL,12,Fchance of saving them. His friend
OL,13,Ftried to save him but couldn't."
OL,26,@nD@[OU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/14
