FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FAbsi had been enjoying a day out with
OL,7,Fthree friends, going for a walk before
OL,8,Fheading to High Dam tarn for a swim as
OL,9,Ftemperatures rose. One says, "We had
OL,10,Fbeen for a two hour walk and the
OL,11,Fweather was nice so we went for a
OL,12,Fswim. When it happened, we didn't see
OL,13,Fany lifebelts ` we definitely think
OL,14,Fthat could be made better."
OL,16,FAdil adds, "We want to do all we can
OL,17,Fto avoid people going through what we
OL,18,Fare."
OL,26,@qD@^OUvD@[O]xD@LOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FAbsi's father Basir and mother Sammi,
OL,7,Fsay they understand their son may have
OL,8,Fsuffered cold water shock, caused by
OL,9,Fsudden immersion in cold water, which
OL,10,Fcan make it difficult to swim, as
OL,11,Fheart rate and blood pressure
OL,12,Fincreases and arms and legs cool as
OL,13,Fthe body tries to keep warm.
OL,15,FHis 22-year old brother Adil, said:
OL,16,F"One of his mates tried to save him
OL,17,Fbut he too began to feel the effects
OL,18,Fof the cold water so had to save
OL,19,Fhimself."
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
