FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe Lake District National Park
OL,7,FAuthority said it is deeply saddened
OL,8,Fby the death and understands the calls
OL,9,Ffor "further equipment in addition to
OL,10,Fthe throw line currently on site." A
OL,11,Fspokesperson said, "We await the
OL,12,Fcoroner's report and will consider any
OL,13,Frecommendations carefully."
OL,15,FThe friends say the funds will go
OL,16,Ftowards:
OL,26,@uD@[O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/14
