FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FAbsi Ahmed was studying business,
OL,7,Feconomics and maths at Blackpool Sixth
OL,8,FForm College and played at Fylde
OL,9,FCricket Club for both junior and
OL,10,Fsenior teams. He made his senior debut
OL,11,Fwith the club's third team last season.
OL,13,FThe club held tributes to him before
OL,14,Fpre-season friendly matches on April
OL,15,F11 and 12, with many of his college
OL,16,Ffriends also taking part in a minute's
OL,17,Fapplause in his memory.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776960675
OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FA club spokesperson said, "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts are with Absi's family and
OL,8,Ffriends at this incredibly difficult
OL,9,Ftime. As a club, we stand beside you
OL,10,Fand send our heartfelt love, strength
OL,11,Fand support. You are part of our Fylde
OL,12,Ffamily, and we are here for you
OL,13,Falways."
OL,15,FAbsi's brother Adil, said: "The house
OL,16,Ffeels empty without him. Absi was very
OL,17,Faffectionate and used to give my mum
OL,18,Fhugs every day. My parents are doing
OL,19,Ftheir best but it's hard to come to
OL,20,Fterms with."
OL,26,@wD@\OU
