OL,3,CTeenager drowned while swimming with
OL,4,Cfriends in High Dam, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe family says they have been
OL,7,Fcomforted by the support they've
OL,8,Freceived from those who knew him.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/14
